he never became exhausted

00:27:36.970 --> 00:27:40.290
from some of the details.

00:27:40.290 --> 00:27:46.790
It's known that " The Tale
of Genji" uses what's known

00:27:46.790 --> 00:27:48.450
as [foreign language spoken]

00:27:48.450 --> 00:27:57.790
which is basically the
transient moment that's captured.

00:27:57.790 --> 00:28:03.520
It can be captured by a
simple expression of oh,

00:28:03.520 --> 00:28:12.810
or ah and so [foreign word] can
also be seen as the magic moments,

00:28:12.810 --> 00:28:17.600
the breathing moment
that will pass eventually

00:28:17.600 --> 00:28:21.400
and I think Gorey really
latched on to that as well.

00:28:21.400 --> 00:28:24.510
He was a very sensitive man.

00:28:24.510 --> 00:28:27.530
He was never married.

