00:30:09.070 --> 00:30:11.670 position:56%
And ballet, of course everyone knows

00:30:11.670 --> 00:30:15.950
that Edward Gorey loved
George Balanchine's work

00:30:15.950 --> 00:30:18.250
at the New York City Ballet.

00:30:19.420 --> 00:30:24.190
And a lot of that flamboyance and
freedom of the characters shows

00:30:24.190 --> 00:30:31.180 position:56%
up in his work not just the
